    "title": "Entry-Level SEO Specialist at Zomato",
    "description": "Join the Zomato family as a SEO Specialist in Lucknow. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Zomato:\nZomato is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Lucknow, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zomato!",
